---
import siteData from '../../data/site.json';
import { Building2 } from 'lucide-svelte';
---
<section class="section section-white">
  <div class="container-tight">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Dikelola Oleh</span>
        <h2 class="heading-title mt-4 mb-6">
          Sahid Hotels & Resorts<br/><em class="text-gold-700">50+ Tahun Track Record</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-body-lg text-ink-500 mb-8">
          Anda mendapat operator kelas dunia. Sahid mengelola 20+ hotel & resort aktif di Indonesia
          dengan standar hospitality bintang 4-5. Villa Anda akan dijalankan dengan SOP yang sama
          dengan hotel-hotel Sahid.
        </p>

        <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-gold-500 pl-6 my-8">
          <p class="font-quote italic text-xl text-forest-700 leading-relaxed">
            "Bagi Saya, Menantu Resort adalah Passive Income Paling Realistis yang Pernah Saya Lihat."
          </p>
          <footer class="mt-4 text-sm text-ink-700">— Ir. H. Dedy Kusnadi, Investor Properti, Jakarta</footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="card accent-line p-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
            <Building2 size="24" class="text-forest-500" strokeWidth="1.5" />
            <span class="eyebrow text-forest-500">Portofolio Sahid</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-body text-ink-500 mb-6">
            Hotel & resort bintangnya:
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            {siteData.manager.notableHotels.slice(0, 8).map((hotel) => (
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-gold-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <span class="text-forest-700">{hotel}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-cream-100 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
            <div>
              <div class="font-display text-2xl text-forest-500 font-bold">50+</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-ink-700">Tahun</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-display text-2xl text-forest-500 font-bold">20+</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-ink-700">Properti</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-display text-2xl text-forest-500 font-bold">5★</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-ink-700">Standar</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
